Package: BPRDcolours
Title: Colour Palletes From The Mignolaverse
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "McCarthy", email = "m.mccarthy1624@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a dataset of predefined color palettes based on the Hellboy and BPRD series, associated color palette functions, 
    and additional functions for generating customized palettes that are on theme. The package also offers functions for applying 
    the palettes to plots made using the 'ggplot2' package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/mccarthy-m-g/BPRDcolours
BugReports: https://github.com/mccarthy-m-g/BPRDcolours/issues
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    ggplot2
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    covr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Language: en-US
